---
title: Balsamic Rosemary Turkey Meatloaves with Garlic Mashed Potatoes & Green Beans Amandine
description: Finding yourself in a meatloaf rut? Enter: this super-savory, aromatic version. We start with ground turkey for a lighter feel, then blend in onion, garlic, fresh rosemary, and panko breadcrumbs. Next, we form the mixture into mini loaves so everyone gets their own. The pièce de résistance? We infuse the usual ketchup glaze with balsamic vinegar for rich tang and caramelization. Add sides of mashed potatoes and almond-studded green beans, and your routine meat-and-potatoes dinner doesn’t stand a chance.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/balsamic-rosemary-turkey-meatloaves-3d89015b.jpg
